body.input:
Product name is: Smartphone Pro X
Product description is: A high-end smartphone with a 6.7-inch OLED display offering vibrant colors and deep contrasts. It comes with 128GB of storage and features an advanced camera system, capable of capturing stunning photos in low light and featuring software enhancements for professional-grade results.

Product name is: Bluetooth Noise-Cancelling Headphones
Product description is: Wireless headphones designed to deliver an immersive audio experience. Equipped with active noise cancelling technology to eliminate ambient sounds, these headphones provide up to 30 hours of battery life. Perfect for long journeys or focused work sessions.

Product name is: Ultra-thin Laptop
Product description is: A sleek, lightweight laptop that blends performance and portability. Featuring a 14-inch display and powered by an Intel i7 processor with 16GB RAM, it handles multitasking effortlessly. Ideal for both professionals on the go and creative enthusiasts.

Product name is: 4K Ultra HD Smart TV
Product description is: Experience stunning 4K visuals on this 65-inch Smart TV, complete with integrated streaming capabilities. Enjoy a seamless viewing experience with HDR support and smart voice controls, making your home entertainment more interactive and enjoyable.

Product name is: Refrigerator with Water Dispenser
Product description is: An energy-efficient refrigerator equipped with a modern water dispenser and ice maker. It's designed to maintain optimal freshness and support versatile storage options with adjustable shelves and humidity-controlled drawers.

Product name is: Espresso Coffee Machine
Product description is: Transform your kitchen into a coffeehouse with this compact espresso machine featuring an intuitive interface. It includes a built-in steam wand for perfectly frothed milk and programmable settings to customize your brew strength and temperature.

Product name is: Cordless Vacuum Cleaner
Product description is: Effortlessly clean your home with this lightweight cordless vacuum, featuring a detachable handheld unit for quick spot cleaning. Equipped with a powerful motor for various surfaces, it’s ideal for both carpeted and hard floors.

Product name is: Electric Mountain Bike
Product description is: Explore new terrains with this all-terrain electric bike, featuring a robust 500W motor. With a 40-mile range on a single charge, it’s perfect for city commuting or adventurous trails. Comes with a durable frame and responsive suspension system.

Product name is: Camping Tent 4-Person
Product description is: Designed for outdoor enthusiasts, this waterproof family tent offers easy setup with its color-coded poles. The spacious interior fits up to four people and includes mesh panels for ventilation and a rainfly for weather protection.

Product name is: Adjustable Dumbbells Set
Product description is: A versatile addition to any home gym, this dumbbell set allows for quick weight adjustments from 5 to 50 lbs. Each dumbbell features an ergonomic handle, ensuring comfort and safety during intense workouts.

Product name is: Yoga Mat with Alignment Lines
Product description is: Enhance your practice with this non-slip yoga mat that includes alignment markers for precise postures. Made from eco-friendly materials, it provides excellent cushioning and support for a variety of exercises.

Product name is: Leather Office Chair
Product description is: Upgrade your workspace with this ergonomic office chair featuring plush leather upholstery. Designed with lumbar support and an adjustable height feature to promote comfort and healthy posture during long hours of work.

Product name is: Modern Bookshelf
Product description is: Add a touch of elegance to any room with this contemporary bookshelf, showcasing a sleek design with five adjustable shelves. Perfect for displaying books, decorative objects, or organizing essentials with style.

Product name is: Smart Home Security Camera
Product description is: Secure your home with this indoor smart security camera, offering real-time alerts and motion detection. It features night vision capabilities and integrates seamlessly with other smart home devices for easy monitoring.

Product name is: Wireless Router with Extended Range
Product description is: Enhance your home network with this dual-band wireless router, designed for extended range and fast connectivity. Includes parental controls and guest access management for a secure browsing experience.

Product name is: Graphic Design Tablet
Product description is: Unleash your creativity with this graphic design tablet, featuring a pressure-sensitive pen for precise control. It offers customizable buttons and a large drawing area, perfect for artists of all skill levels.

Product name is: Men's Running Shoes
Product description is: Engineered for performance, these men's running shoes offer a lightweight build with breathable mesh fabric. The cushioned sole provides excellent support and shock absorption, ideal for runners seeking comfort and speed.

Product name is: Women's Winter Jacket
Product description is: Stay warm in style with this insulated winter jacket, featuring a detachable hood and a water-resistant exterior. Its tailored fit and cozy lining make it a fashionable choice for cold weather protection.

Product name is: Organic Skincare Set
Product description is: Indulge your skin with this set of organic skincare products, including a gentle cleanser, refreshing toner, and hydrating moisturizer. Formulated with natural ingredients, it's ideal for promoting healthy, radiant skin.

Product name is: Aromatherapy Essential Oil Diffuser
Product description is: Create a serene atmosphere with this ultrasonic essential oil diffuser, featuring customizable LED lights and timer settings. It's perfect for enhancing relaxation and improving air quality with your favorite scents.
